atrick Jack Rhodes Dawson|Dawson]]|GBR|2013 Summer Universiade}}<br />'''L''' 000\u2013110\n|colspan=4 align=center|Did not advance\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Miroljub Ivezi\u0107]]\n|align=left|[[Judo at the 2013 Summer Universiade \u2013 Men's welterweight|Welterweight]]\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Wen-shun Wu|Wu]]|TPE|2013 Summer Universiade}}<br />'''W''' 001\u2013000\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Laszlo Csoknyai|Csoknyai]]|HUN|2013 Summer Universiade}}<br />'''L''' 000\u2013101\n|colspan=4 align=center|Did not advance\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Aleksandar Kukolj]]\n|align=left|[[Judo at the 2013 Summer Universiade \u2013 Men's middleweight|Middleweight]]\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Jakub Zarzeczy|Zarzeczy]]|POL|2013 Summer Universiade}}<br />'''W''' 100\u2013000\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Alexandr Jure\u010dka|Jure\u010dka]]|CZE|2013 Summer Universiade}}<br />'''L''' 000\u2013100\n|colspan=4 align=center|Did not advance\n|}\n\n;Repechage rounds\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Athlete\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Event\n!First repechage <br />round\n!Second repechage <br />round\n!Repechage <br />quarterfinals\n!Repechage <br />semifinals\n!colspan=2|Bronze final\n|-\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Rank\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Miroljub Ivezi\u0107]]\n|align=left|[[Judo at the 2013 Summer Universiade \u2013 Men's welterweight|Welterweight]]\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Andranik Chaparyan|Chaparyan]]|ARM|2013 Summer Universiade}}<br />'''W''' 011\u2013010\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Giovanni Battista Maria Carollo|Carollo]]|ITA|2013 Summer Universiade}}<br />'''W''' 110\u2013000\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Haiyuan Gao|Gao]]|CHN|2013 Summer Universiade}}<br />'''L''' 000\u2013101\n|colspan=2 align=center|Did not advance\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Aleksandar Kukolj]]\n|align=left|[[Judo at the 2013 Summer Universiade \u2013 Men's middlewe