kola Dedovi\u0107|Dedovi\u0107]] 5\n| goals2 = [[Aleksei Rizov-Alenichev|Rizov-Alenichev]] 5\n}}\n\n;Bronze Medal Match\n{{waterpolobox\n| date = 17 July 2013\n| time = 11:15\n| team1 = {{wp-rt|ITA}} \n| score1 = 10\n| team2 = '''{{wp|SRB}}''' {{bronze3}}\n| score2 = '''12'''\n| report = [http://universiade2013.sportresult.com/eurosport/en/-240/Root/ViewPdf/WPM400102_C73_1.0.PDF Report]\n| location = Burevestnik Swimming Pool\n| referees = Szekely (HUN), Franulovi\u0107 (CRO)\n| Q1 = 1\u2013'''5'''\n| Q2 = '''4'''\u20132\n| Q3 = '''3'''\u20132\n| Q4 = 2\u2013'''3'''\n| OT = \n| goals1 = [[Alessandro di Somma|di Somma]], [[Stefano Luongo|Luongo]] 3\n| goals2 = [[Sr\u0111an Vuksanovi\u0107|Vuksanovi\u0107]] 5\n}}\n\n==Weightlifting ==\n{{Main article|Weightlifting at the 2013 Summer Universiade}}\n\n;Women\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n!rowspan=2|Athlete\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!colspan=2|Snatch\n!colspan=2|Clean & Jerk\n!rowspan=2|Total\n!rowspan=2|Rank\n|- style=\"font-size:95%\"\n!Result\n!Rank\n!Result\n!Rank\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Silvana Vukas]]\n|align=left|[[Weightlifting at the 2013 Summer Universiade \u2013 Women's 63 kg|63 kg]]\n|71\n|16\n|95\n|15\n|166\n|15\n|}\n\n== Wrestling ==\n{{Main article|Wrestling at the 2013 Summer Universiade}}\n\n{{smalldiv|1=<nowiki/>\n'''Key''':\n* {{abbr|VT|Victory by Fall}} - [[Pin (amateur wrestling)|Victory by Fall]].\n* {{abbr|PP|Decision by Points - the loser with technical points}} - Decision by Points - the loser with technical points.\n* {{abbr|PO|Decision by Points - the loser without technical points}} - Decision by Points - the loser without technical points.\n}}\n\n;Greco-Roman\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n!rowspan=2|Athlete\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!Qualification Round\n!Round of 16\n!Quarterfinal\n!Semifinal\n!Repechage 1\n!Repechage 2\n!colspan=2|Final / {{abbr|BM|Bronze medal match}}\n|- style=\"font-size: 95%\"\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Opp