 Efendiev]] || [[Wrestling at the 2013 Summer Universiade|Wrestling]] || [[Wrestling at the 2013 Summer Universiade \u2013 Men's Freestyle 74 kg|\u221274 kg]] || {{dts|12 July}}\n|}\n\n== Athletics ==\n{{Main article|Athletics at the 2013 Summer Universiade}}\n\n;Field events\n{| class=wikitable style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n!rowspan=2|Athlete\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!colspan=2|Qualification\n!colspan=2|Final\n|- \n!Distance\n!Position\n!Distance\n!Position\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Milo\u0161 Todosijevi\u0107]]\n|align=left|[[Athletics at the 2013 Summer Universiade \u2013 Men's high jump|Men's high jump]]\n|2.15\n|11 '''q'''\n|2.10\n|13\n|}\n\n==  Badminton ==\n{{Main article|Badminton at the 2013 Summer Universiade}}\n\n;Men\n{|class=\"wikitable\" border=\"1\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n!rowspan=2|Athlete\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!Preliminary Round \n!Round of 128\n!Round of 64\n!Round of 32\n!Round of 16\n!Quarterfinals\n!Semifinals\n!colspan=2|Final\n|-\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Rank\n|-\n|[[Ilija Pavlovi\u0107]]\n|[[Badminton at the 2013 Summer Universiade \u2013 Men's singles|Men's singles]]\n|align=center|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Kenta Nishimoto|Nishimoto]]|JPN|2013 Summer Universiade}}<br />'''L''' 18\u201321, 6\u201321\n|align=center colspan=8|Did not advance\n|}\n\n;Women\n{|class=\"wikitable\" border=\"1\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n!rowspan=2|Athlete\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!Preliminary Round\n!Round of 32\n!Round of 16\n!Quarterfinals\n!Semifinals\n!colspan=2|Final\n|-\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Rank\n|-\n|[[Milica Simi\u0107]]\n|[[Badminton at the 2013 Summer Universiade \u2013 Women's singles|Women's singles]]\n|align=center|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Fabienne Deprez|Deprez]]|GER|2013 Su