760|accessdate=October 12, 2019}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"3\" |''7''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"[[Panini (song)|Panini]]\"\n| 2019\n| 5 || 2 || 15 || 8 || 28 || 18 || 26 || 14 || 42 || 21\n|\n|\n* RIAA: 4\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\" />\n* ARIA: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2019/12/aria-chart-watch-554/|title=ARIA Chart Watch #554|publisher=auspOp|date=December 7, 2019|accessdate=December 7, 2019}}</ref>\n* BPI: Gold<ref name=\"ReferenceA\" />\n* IFPI DEN: Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.dk/node/9154|title=Lil Nas X \"Panini\"|publisher=[[IFPI Denmark]]|accessdate=April 21, 2020}}</ref>\n* MC: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"MC\" />\n* RMNZ: Gold<ref>{{cite certification|region=New Zealand|type=single|artist=Lil Nas X|title=Panini|recent=website|id=4746|accessdate=September 14, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Rodeo (Lil Nas X and Cardi B song)#Lil Nas X and Nas remix|Rodeo]]\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with [[Cardi B]] or [[Nas]])</span>\n| 2020\n| 22 || 12 || 72 || 44 || \u2014 || 35 || \u2014 || \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Rodeo\" did not enter the [[Official New Zealand Music Chart|NZ Top 40 Singles Chart]], but peaked at number 27 on the NZ Hot Singles Chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4817|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=February 10, 2020|accessdate=February 8, 2020}}</ref>}} || \u2014 || 55\n|\n|\n* RIAA: Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\"/>\n* MC: Gold<ref name=\"MC\"/>\n|-\n| colspan=\"15\" style=\"font-size:90%\" | \"\u2014\" denotes a recording that did not chart or was not released in that territory.\n|}\n\n===Other charted songs===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:14em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"4\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|- style=\"font-size:smaller;\"\n! scope=\"col\" style=\