00|US]]<br/><ref name=\"Hot 100\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8506256/lil-nas-x-old-town-road-number-one-hot-100|title= 'Lil Nas X's \"Old Town Road\" Leaps to No. 1 on the Hot 100|work=Billboard|last=Trust|first=Gary|date=April 8, 2019|accessdate=April 9, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/8530747/lizzo-truth-hurts-number-one-fourth-week-hot-100|title=Lizzo's 'Truth Hurts' Tops Billboard Hot 100 For Fourth Week, Lil Nas X's 'Panini' Hits Top 10|work=Billboard|last=Trust|first=Gary|date=September 23, 2019|accessdate=September 24, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs|US<br>R&B<br>/HH]]<br/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/r-b-hip-hop-songs/2019-04-13|title=Top R&B/Hip-Hop Songs: April 13, 2019|work=Billboard|accessdate=April 9, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br/><ref name=\"ARIA\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=March 9, 2020|accessdate=March 7, 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[Canadian Hot 100|CAN]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/search?artist=Lil+Nas+X&chart_name=Billboard+Canadian+Hot+100|title=Chart Search: Canadian Hot 100|work=Billboard|accessdate=October 1, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[Hitlisten|DEN]]<br/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://danishcharts.dk/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Lil+Nas+X|title=Discography Lil Nas X|website=danishcharts.dk|accessdate=February 8, 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[Irish Recorded Music Association|IRE]]<br/><ref name=\"IRE\">{{cite web|url=http://irma.ie/index.cfm?page=irish-charts&chart=Singles|title=IRMA \u2013 Irish Charts|publisher=[[Irish Recorded Music Association]]|accessdate=June 29, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[VG-lista|NOR]]<br><ref>Peaks in Norway:\n* \"Old Town Road\": {{cite web|url=http://www.vglista.no/topplister/topp-20-single-2019-15/|title=VG-lista \u2013 Topp 20 Single uke 15, 2019|publisher=[[VG-lista]]|accessdate=April 13, 2019}}\n* \"Panini\": {{cite web|url=http://www.vglista.no/topplister/topp-20-single-2019-40/|title=VG-lista \u2013 Topp 20 Single uke 40, 2019|publisher=VG-lista|accessdate=October 5, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[Official New Zealand Music Chart|NZ]]<br><ref name=\"NZ\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[Sverigetopplistan|SWE]]<br><ref>Peaks in Sweden:\n* \"Old Town Road\": {{cite web|url=https://www.sverigetopplistan.se/chart/41?dspy=2019&dspp=16|title=Veckolista Singlar, vecka 16|publisher=[[Sverigetopplistan]]|accessdate=April 27, 2019}}\n* \"Panini\": {{cite web|url=https://www.sverigetopplistan.se/chart/41?dspy=2019&dspp=28|title=Veckolista Singlar, vecka 28|publisher=Sverigetopplistan|accessdate=July 12, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;\"| [[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br/><ref name=\"UK\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Donald Trump\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/3Soar7Pohekpsdv3u3G7Yf|title=Donald Trump by Lil Nas X on Spotify|last=|first=|date=|website=Spotify|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"7\" |2018\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\n|\n| rowspan=\"2\" |''Nasarati''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Thanos\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/1W3OqQiXDvIQfsHwPIOEP8|title=Thanos (Blow It) by Lil Nas X on Spotify|last=|first=|date=|website=Spotify|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Rookie\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/7oXpStinOZ5zzUkF9CjKEx|title=Rookie by Lil Nas X on Spotify|last=|f