{"title_page": "Saudi Arabia at the 2018 Asian Games", "text_new": "{{Infobox country at games\n| NOC          = KSA\n| NOCname      = [[Saudi Arabian Olympic Committee]]\n| oldcode      = \n| year         = 2018\n| date         = {{Start date|18|8||df=y}} \u2013 {{End date|2|9||df=y}} \n| games        = Asian Games\n| location     = [[Jakarta]] and [[Palembang]]\n| competitors  = \n| sports       = \n| flagbearer   = [[Ali Yousef Alothman]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.spa.gov.sa/viewstory.php?lang=ar&newsid=1799355|title=\u0631\u064a\u0627\u0636\u064a / \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0626\u064a\u0633 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0646\u062f\u0648\u0646\u064a\u0633\u064a \u064a\u0641\u062a\u062a\u062d \u0631\u0633\u0645\u064a\u0627\u064b \u062f\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0644\u0639\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0622\u0633\u064a\u0648\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0627\u0645\u0646\u0629 \u0639\u0634\u0631\u0629 \"\u062c\u0627\u0643\u0631\u062a\u0627 2018 \u201c|date=18 August 2018|trans-title=Indonesian President officially opens the 18th Asian Games \"Jakarta 2018\"|language=Arabic|website=www.spa.gov.sa/|publisher=[[Saudi Press Agency]]|access-date=19 August 2018}}</ref>\n| officials    = \n| gold         = 1\n| silver       = 2\n| bronze       = 3\n| rank         = 25\n| appearances  = auto\n| seealso      = \n| website      = [http://www.olympic.sa/ www.olympic.sa]\n}}\n\n'''[[Saudi Arabia]]''' competed at the '''[[2018 Asian Games]]''' in [[Jakarta]] and [[Palembang]], [[Indonesia]], from 18 August to 2 September 2018.<ref>{{cite web |title=Participants |url=https://www.asiangames2018.id/participants |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711063153/https://www.asiangames2018.id/participants |url-status=dead |publisher=2018 Asian Games |archivedate=11 July 2018 |accessdate=21 July 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Medalists==\n{{Further information|2018 Asian Games medal table}}\n\nThe following Saudi Arabia competitors won medals at the Games.\n{{col-begin}}\n|  style=\"text-align