es\n!Rank\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Rank\n|-\n|align=left|Hamza Wazzan<br />Ajwad Wazzan<br />Maan Arshad<br />Nawaf Alsalem<br />Meshal Albarrak\n|align=left|''Wickychi<br />Ajwad<br />Fear<br />Mimic<br />Mishal''\n|align=left|[[Esports at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 League of Legends tournament|League of Legends]]\n|align=left|{{flagIOC2|TPE|2018 Asian Games}}: '''L''' 0\u20132<br />{{flagIOC2|PAK|2018 Asian Games}}: '''W''' 2\u20130<br />{{flagIOC2|INA|2018 Asian Games}}: '''W''' 2\u20130\n|2 '''Q'''\n|{{flagIOC2|KOR|2018 Asian Games}}<br />'''L''' 0\u20132\n|{{flagIOC2|TPE|2018 Asian Games}}<br />'''L''' 1\u20133\n|4\n|}\n\n== Football ==\n{{main article|Football at the 2018 Asian Games}}\n\nSaudi Arabia drawn in group F at the Games.<ref>{{cite news |first=Kevin |last=Affleck |title=Saudi Arabia drawn in group with Iran and North Korea at Asian Games |url=http://www.arabnews.com/node/1334381/sport |publisher=[[Arab News]] |date=6 July 2018 |access-date=2 August 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"drw\">{{Cite news |title=\u0627\u0644\u0633\u0639\u0648\u062f\u064a\u0629 \u0641\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062c\u0645\u0648\u0639\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0627\u062f\u0633\u0629 \u0628\u062f\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0644\u0639\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0622\u0633\u064a\u0648\u064a\u0629 |url=http://www.kooora.com/%5C?n=717660&o=n1005434 |publisher=Kooora |date=5 July 2018 |access-date=16 August 2018 |language=Arabic}}</ref>\n\n;Summary\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:90%;text-align:center\n!rowspan=2|Team\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!colspan=4|Group Stage\n!Round of 16\n!Quarterfinal\n!Semifinal\n!colspan=2|Final / {{abbr|BM|Bronze medal game}}\n|-style=font-size:95%\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Rank\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Rank\n|-\n|align=left|[[Saudi Arabia national under-23 football team|Saudi Arabia men's]]\n|align=left|[[Football at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's tournament|Men's tournament]]\n|{{fbu|23|IRI}}<br />'''D''' 0\u20130\n|{{fbu|23|MYA}}<br />'''W''' 3\u20130\n|{{fbu|23|PRK}}<br />'''L''' 0\u20133\n|3 '''Q'''\n|{{fbu|23|CHN}}<br />'''W''' 4\u20133\n|{{fbu|23|JPN}}<br />'''L''' 1\u20132\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|8\n|}\n\n=== Men's tournament ===\n{{main|Football at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's tournament}}\n\n;Roster\n{{2018 Asian Games Saudi Arabia men's football team roster}}\n\n;Group F\n{{2018 Asian Games men's football group F standings}}\n\n{{2018 Asian Games men's football game F1}}\n----\n{{2018 Asian Games men's football game F4}}\n----\n{{2018 Asian Games men's football game F6}}\n\n;Round of 16\n{{2018 Asian Games men's football game RD5}}\n\n;Quarter-finals\n{{2018 Asian Games men's football game QF3}}\n\n== Gymnastics ==\n{{main article|Gymnastics at the 2018 Asian Games}}\n\n== Handball ==\n{{main article|Handball at the 2018 Asian Games}}\n\nSaudi Arabia men's team will compete in group C at the Games.<ref name=\"drw\"/><ref>{{Cite web |title=18th Asian Games 2018 Men's Handball Event |url=https://www.asianhandball.org/images/results/18ASIANGAMES2018/Draw%20Results%20Men.jpeg |publisher=[[Asian Handball Federation]] |access-date=2 August 2018}}</ref>\n\n;Summary\n{{\n|1=<nowiki/>\n'''Key''':\n* ET \u2013 After [[Overtime (sports)#Handball|extra time]]\n* P \u2013 Match decided by penalty-shootout.\n}}\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:90%;text-align:center\n|-\n!rowspan=2|Team\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!Preliminary\n!rowspan=2|Standing\n!Main / {{abbr|Class.|Classification round}}\n!rowspan=2|Rank /<br />Standing\n!Semifinals / {{abbr|Pl.|Placement semifinal}} \n!colspan=2|Final / {{abbr|BM|Bronze medal match}} / {{abbr|Pl.|Placement match}}\n|- style=\"font-size:95%\"\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Rank\n|- \n|align=left|[[Saudi Arabia national handball team|Saudi Arabia men's]]\n|align=lef