 for Saudi Arabia |url=http://www.arabnews.com/node/1361361/sport |publisher=[[Arab News]] |date=24 August 2018 |accessdate=29 August 2018}}</ref>\n\n;Men\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:90%;text-align:center\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Athlete\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Event\n!colspan=2|Qualification\n!colspan=2|Final\n|- style=\"font-size:95%\"\n!Points\n!Rank\n!Points\n!Rank\n|-\n|align=left|[[Atallah Al-Anazi]]\n|align=left rowspan=2|[[Shooting at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 10 metre air pistol|10 m air pistol]]\n|573\n|17\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|Safar Al-Dosari\n|560\n|32\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|Mesfer Al-Ammari\n|align=left rowspan=2|[[Shooting at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 10 metre air rifle|10 m air rife]]\n|617.3\n|21\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|Hussain Al-Harbi\n|616.8\n|24\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|'''Hussain Al-Harbi'''\n|align=left rowspan=2|[[Shooting at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 300 metre standard rifle|300 m standard rifle]]\n|colspan=2 {{n/a}}\n|568\n|{{silver02}}\n|-\n|align=left|Abdulrahman Al-Juhaydili\n|colspan=2 {{n/a}}\n|557\n|9\n|-\n|align=left|[[Saeed Al-Mutairi]]\n|align=left|[[Shooting at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's skeet|Skeet]]\n|122\n|4 '''Q'''\n|31\n|4\n|}\n\n== Swimming ==\n{{main article|Swimming at the 2018 Asian Games}}\n\n;Men\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:90%;text-align:center\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Athlete\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Event\n!colspan=\"2\"|Heats\n!colspan=\"2\"|Final\n|-style=\"font-size:95%\"\n!Time\n!Rank\n!Time\n!Rank\n|-\n|align=left rowspan=3|Yousif Habib Bu Arish\n|align=left|[[Swimming at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 50 metre freestyle|50 m freestyle]]\n|24.39\n|33\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|[[Swimming at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 50 metre butterfly|50 m butterfly]]\n|25.74\n|30\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|[[Swimming at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 100 metre butterfly|100 m butterfly]]\n|57.84\n|27\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|}\n\n==Taekwondo==\n{{main article|Taekwondo at the 2018 Asian Games}}\n\n;Poomsae\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:90%;text-align:center\n!rowspan=2|Athlete\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!Round of 16\n!Quarterfinal\n!Semifinal\n!colspan=2|Final\n|-style=font-size:95%\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Rank\n|-\n|align=left|Wahid Moghis\n|align=left|[[Taekwondo at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's individual poomsae|Men's individual]]\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|Hu Mingda|CHN|2018 Asian Games}}<br />'''L''' 7.86\u20138.34\n|colspan=4|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|Wahid Moghis<br />Essa Al-Shaikh<br />Mohammed Al-Mustafa\n|align=left|[[Taekwondo at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's team poomsae|Men's team]]\n|{{flagIOC2|PHI|2018 Asian Games}}<br />'''L''' 7.64\u20138.18\n|colspan=4|Did not advance\n|}\n\n;Kyorugi\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:90%;text-align:center\n!rowspan=2|Athlete\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!Round of 32\n!Round of 16\n!Quarterfinal\n!Semifinal\n!colspan=2|Final\n|-style=font-size:95%\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Opposition<br />score\n!Rank\n|-\n|align=left|Ali Asiri\n|align=left|[[Taekwondo at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 58 kg|Men's \u221258 kg]]\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|align=left|Hamad Al-Mabrouk\n|align=left|[[Taekwondo at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 63 kg|Men's \u221263 kg]]\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Tawin Hanprab]]|THA|2018 Asian Games}}<br />\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|align=left|Ghazi Al-Asmari\n|align=left|[[Taekwondo at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 68 kg|Men's \u221268 kg]]\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|Sonexay Mangkheua|LAO|2018 Asian Games}}<br />\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|align=left|Saud Al-Muwallad\n|align=left|[[Taekwondo at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 80 kg|Men's \u221280 kg]]\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|Nurlan Myrzabayev|KAZ|2018 Asian Games}}<br />\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\