zy Al-Duhami]]'''\n|align=left|TED\n|align=left rowspan=4|[[Equestrian at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Individual jumping|Individual]]\n|0.00\n|1\n|0\n|0.00\n|1 '''Q'''\n|1\n|1.00\n|1 '''Q'''\n|0\n|1.00\n|1 '''Q'''\n|4\n|5.00\n|{{bronze03}}\n|-\n|align=left|[[Khaled Al-Eid]]\n|align=left|Kayenne of de Rocky Mounten\n|1.50\n|5\n|4\n|5.50\n|11 '''Q'''\n|0\n|5.50\n|8 '''Q'''\n|8\n|13.50\n|11\n|colspan=3|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|Khaled Al-Mobty\n|align=left|Dessert Storm II\n|0.40\n|2\n|0\n|0.40\n|2 '''Q'''\n|4\n|4.40\n|7 '''Q'''\n|5\n|9.40\n|8 '''Q'''\n|6\n|15.40\n|8\n|-\n|align=left|[[Abdullah Al-Sharbatly]]\n|align=left|Carrera\n|4.19 #\n|14\n|colspan=3|Eliminated\n|colspan=9|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|'''[[Abdullah Al-Sharbatly]]<br>[[Khaled Al-Eid]]<br>Khaled Al-Mobty<br>[[Ramzy Al-Duhami]]'''\n|align=left|''See above''\n|align=left|[[Equestrian at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Team jumping|Team]]\n|1.90\n|1\n|4\n|5.90\n|1 '''Q'''\n|5\n|10.90\n|{{gold01}}\n|colspan=6 {{n/a}}\n|}\n<small># \u2013 indicates that the score of this rider does not count in the team competition, since only the best three results of a team are counted.</small>\n\n== Esports (demonstration) ==\n{{main article|Esports at the 2018 Asian Games}}\n\n;Clash Royale<ref>{{cite news|first=Ady |last=Sesotya |title=Esport - India Vs Arab Saudi |url=https://www.antarafoto.com/bisnis/v1535378135/esport-india-vs-arab-saudi |publisher=[[Antara (news agency)|Antara]] |date=27 August 2018 |access-date=7 January 2019 |language=Indonesian}}</ref>\n{|class=wikitable style=\"font-size:90%; text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Athlete\n!rowspan=\"2\"|ID\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Event\n!Round 1\n!Round 2\n!Round 3\n!Loser<br>round 1\n!Loser<br>round 2\n!Loser<br>round 3\n!Semifinal\n!colspan=2|Final\n|-style=\"font-size:95%\"\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<br />Score\n!Opposition<b